Dan walaupun saya menghargai
bagaimana anda membantu Gun-woo.

163
00:08:55,076 --> 00:08:55,910
Awak faham?

164
00:08:56,744 --> 00:08:58,454
Ya, saya lakukan.

165
00:09:00,331 --> 00:09:02,542
